Chat Application Part 3
---

NAME: Esamisipho Ndiko
Student Number: ST10531476
Module: PROG5121
---

In Part 3, the ChatApp was upgraded to track information like sent, skipped, and saved messages, 
as well as unique message IDs and security codes (hashes), using five internal lists. 
The app now automatically loads previously saved messages from a JSON file.
A new "Stored Messages" option was also added to the main menu, allowing users to view all saved messages, 
find the longest one, search by ID or phone number, delete a message using its hash, or pull up a full report of all sent data. 
Finally, six new tests were written to ensure these search and list features work perfectly. 
The entire app was tested from start to finish, and everything runs smoothly and passes all automatic checks on GitHub.
